sub_title: International MBA Candidate, RSM School of Management
summary:
Passionate, results-oriented Senior Program Manager with proven track record of developing collaborations between leading members of pharma-industry, academic and nonprofit research organizations in global health initiatives.

I am currently studying for my MBA at Rotterdam School of Management, The Netherlands and will be available to work in January 2024. I am interested in working at the intersection of global health and climate action to strategically address the needs of the world's most vulnerable populations.

MBA | Sustainability | Program Management | Global Health | Health Finance | Cross-sector Collaboration | Partnership Development | Alliance Management | Impact Reporting | Peer-reviewed Publications | Grant Writing | Strategic Market-Access
